body:
Hello everyone, today I am happy to announce that I will be doing a (very late) giveaway.

*Since this was a Christmas giveaway, there is no need to subscribe to my channel. This giveaway is simply for fun. :)*

I was planning on doing a giveaway for Christmas, but I unfortunately forgot to, as I was very busy with friends and family during the Winter break, but I was reminded of the giveaway when I saw vladthegreat100's giveaway earlier today.

I would like to point out that the alt will not be new. It belonged to a friend and he stopped playing Minecraft a few months ago, and I got his permission to give it away.

Anyways, there is no reason why I am doing this giveaway, so please put your name down if you wish to enter the giveaway. Again, this giveaway was originally meant to be done at Christmastime, so I am very sorry that I am late with it. I intended to announce a winner by the New Year. If you are not entering, you may still put the name of another player to receive this alternate account.

The winner will be chosen on the 17th of January. However, if most people enter early, the winner may be announced earlier.

*note*: This giveaway is for Avicus players only. I did not post a YouTube video regarding this giveaway, so your chance is a bit larger this time.

Merry Christmas everyone, and I hope you all had a Happy New Year!
